QuestData.Title: Alpaca Soul
QuestData.Description: <The Alpaca Soul is wary and alert. The shape of the alpaca will be yours to call upon.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring the Alpaca Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Bring the Alpaca Soul to Lady Muunn in the Heart of the Forest.
QuestData.RewardText: Ah, the alpaca. This shape is now yours to call upon.
